[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第五",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大試鴻臚少卿",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明教大師臣法賢奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時摩賀曩摩說此偈已，即往北門高聲問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此有何人不睡守護？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」甘露飯王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我於此處不睡守護。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若不睡守護無諸過失。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「怖睡如山嶮，　　亦如汎河海；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一心防難危，　　止睡亦如是。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時摩賀曩摩說此偈已，即往市肆街巷處處巡行，覺察眾人止睡守護，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「依法離非法，　　實言勿妄言；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "淨飯王最上，　　止睡令守護。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時摩賀曩摩說此偈已，天色將曉詣淨飯王前，而白王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「過一晝夜，內外安靜無諸魔難。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b24_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願大王，更勅軍眾用心守護過七晝夜，令彼太子定得輪王之位。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是防護至六晝夜。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時忉利天主，觀太子意欲往道場，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉大丈夫！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　牟尼釋師子；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "必捨王宮殿，　　趣求山野處。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "圓滿六波羅，　　成就無上智；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拔濟於群生，　　究竟至彼岸。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時悉達多太子，與諸宮嬪作於娛樂，而忽思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今雖有耶輸陀羅、娛閉迦、蜜里誐惹，如是夫人及六萬婇女，若無男女便去修行，眾人俱言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『悉達多太子非是丈夫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」出別之後，即令耶輸身有懷妊。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是太子為諸宮嬪說：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「緣生幻有，生死輪迴，若不息心，無有窮盡；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c08_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若與女人同其床座，如足履火速得大苦，是故我今而生厭離。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語時有一妓女，口吐涎沫，手足紛紜，髮髻散亂，迷悶倒地。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸宮人驚怖異常，太子見之深生傷愍，歎言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「苦哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何有此死相不祥。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須臾變壞生惡相，　　手足紛紜涎沫流；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "覩此無常苦惱身，　　是故我今求解脫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時太子說此偈已，觀諸眾生，無有我、人、眾生、壽者堅實之相，如入尸陀林，無所愛樂，如履淤泥，唯增臭惡，如養毒蛇，終無所益，如電如夢，如沫如泡，根本無明覆而不覺。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c19_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是觀已，時淨飯王自說其四夢：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一夢滿月有其蝕障；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二夢日出復於東沒；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三夢大人眾來禮拜；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四夢自身笑而復哭。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耶輸陀羅亦說八夢：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一夢上族離散；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二夢吉祥座破；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三夢腕釧損墜；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四夢牙齒墮落；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五夢髻髮亂垂；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六夢吉祥雲出於宮舍；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七夢滿月有其蝕障；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八夢日出未高復於東沒。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即時太子復自思惟，曾作五夢：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一夢床座如妙高山，坐臥自在；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二夢兩手左托東海，右托西海，復以二足垂南海中；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三夢花果、樹木及諸藥草長至天界；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0945c29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四夢大身飛禽其類甚眾，形白頭黑，及諸小鳥種種顏色，四方而來都至面前，變為一色而禮其足；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五夢大石山上經行顧望。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子自心思念：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我夢如此，定得捨俗，證大菩提。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時耶輸陀羅，思前八夢，告請太子占其吉凶。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一夢上族離散，宗姓團聚未始暫分；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二夢吉祥座破，座今如故；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三夢腕釧損墜，見在汝臂；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四夢牙齒墮落，非有墮者；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五夢髮亂垂，孰覩垂髮？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a08_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六夢吉祥雲出宮，夫為吉祥我又在宮；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七夢月有蝕障，今在天上何有障耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八夢日出未高復於東沒，此時夜半日又未出。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所夢無惡汝何憂疑？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此之八夢，當應是我出家之兆。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即告耶輸陀羅：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今當為一切眾生往彼山間，志求涅槃解脫之法。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」耶輸陀羅言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如夫所志我亦隨往。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時帝釋天主及梵天王告太子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "速捨五欲早出宮殿，明相現前證一切智。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我在深宮如虎入穽，象、馬、車、步四兵圍繞，宮殿門戶，並皆鎖閉，處處懸鈴，警覺守護，云何而出？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」帝釋告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「但念過去無量阿僧祇劫所行行願，為斷眾苦，度脫世間。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語時，四大天等以威神力，令彼眾人不能為障。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即時帝釋化一寶階，告般唧迦夜叉主言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「聖者菩薩現處高樓，汝以寶階於前迎接。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」夜叉聞已，依教奉行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩下之即覓飡那令被馬王，尋見飡那正當眠睡，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "飡那汝速起，　　被我馬王迦蹉迦；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乘入諸佛修行山，　　求證牟尼無上覺。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說此偈已，飡那從睡眠覺，即起合掌告菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「事無倉卒，何於夜半急要馬王欲乘遠去？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "況此宮禁，且無兵難、賊難及水火之難，云何如此？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝自昔來甞奉驅馳，云何於今而不相順？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」飡那白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今當半夜，真偽難分，慮有不虞以招大罪。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩聞已默然思念，恐人知覺自往中厩。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時天主帝釋手執火炬，引路前行，至其厩門牽致馬王，馬即驚駭雙足跑地。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時菩薩舉萬字福相、百千威德之手，作無畏印，摩馬王頂告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦蹉迦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "與我有緣，若能送我雪山之中諸佛行處，證得無上菩提之果，降大法雨普潤世間，一切有情皆獲利樂，汝福無量。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時迦蹉迦即受教旨，身足不動。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時復有四大天子：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一名俱羅；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二名烏波俱羅；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三名波囉拏；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四名波囉拏舍嚩帝。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此四天子至菩薩前，合掌恭敬告菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今知出外修菩提行，我等四天願欲隨從。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝有力耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第一天子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有大地之土可以負行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第二天子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有大海、江河可以負行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第三天子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有一切山嶽可以負行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b20_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第四天子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有大地、山嶽及河海等，俱可負行而無疲困。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩聞已，即以神力移足躡地，地大振動，四大天子住立不能而各驚怪：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「誰知菩薩有斯威力，我等四天云何懺謝？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時飡那見是神力，即牽馬王詣菩薩前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時大威德諸天，及諸龍神傷愛別離，於上空中啼泣下淚。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "飡那言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何空中無雲下雨？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此非降雨。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我將出外，天龍傷別，啼泣雨淚。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」飡那聽受住立合掌。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩即時深思佛功德威儀利樂之法，復思父母養育慈愛顧復之恩，如不告辭有虧孝行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念已，即入殿內，見淨飯王正當睡眠，右繞一匝合掌啟白：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我於此時往雪山中求無上道，度脫世間生、老、病、死，令諸眾生得大解脫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」言已而辭。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c05_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有釋種摩賀曩摩，瞻見太子，戀慕憂惱悲泣涕淚：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何因業輕捨王宮？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我為利益一切眾生，求成佛果。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩白云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「王勅我輩長時警護，無令太子暫出宮禁。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我於往昔發菩提心，經三大阿僧祇劫，歷修萬行求無上覺，欲度眾生，今此王宮非我所止。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩聞是語時，倍復憂惱涕淚悲泣，發麤澁言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「苦哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苦哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我淨飯王所望不就，致令大子棄捨深宮欲出遠行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時耶輸陀羅聞是語已，驚疑惶怖，迷悶倒地，良久乃蘇。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "告太子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「緣何今日捨我而去？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」娛閉迦，蜜里誐惹，及諸宮嬪悲淚前行，告淨飯王：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子無故，欲離宮寢往彼山野，如鬼魅所著無以遮止，唯王當嚴勗勿令遽往。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王既聞已欲行誡勅，帝釋梵王與諸天子，接迎菩薩即出城外。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩右邊色界天子善現威儀，菩薩左邊欲界天子手執幢幡，有無數天樂導引前行，有百千天子，於虛空中雨優鉢羅花、俱母那花、白蓮花，及曼陀羅花；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復雨沈香、末香、旃檀之香，種種上妙衣服；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有天子歌舞作唱，復有天子手捧馬足，瞻仰菩薩一心隨行，俱吠囉等無量諸天恭敬圍繞，須臾之間至雪山中，去迦毘羅城一十二由旬。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時天主帝釋及大梵天王等，合掌白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0946c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等諸天發精進心，隨侍菩薩來至山中，若我菩薩成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提時，願垂攝受度脫我等。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」住立右邊一心瞻仰。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩即時為說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我得最上道，　　一切佛行處；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "度脫於汝等，　　及彼諸有情。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說此語已即脫寶冠上妙衣服，告飡那曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「將我衣服及彼馬王歸奉父王，若不證菩提誓不迴也。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝將馬王及寶衣，　　速歸本國迦毘羅；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我住雪山修梵行，　　菩提未證而未歸。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時菩薩說此偈已，飡那聞之而復悲泣，白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此山中多有虎、狼、師子諸惡禽獸，菩薩一身云何可止？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此山野中皆有叢林、荊棘、土石、磽确，菩薩旦暮云何經行？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「飡那！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝何愚迷，眾生之身業惑所感，四大和合性相違反，老、病、死、苦，如至身時，非擇尊貴上族，富豪貧賤，端正醜陋，少壯老年，冤親人我，速歸散壞，俱受無常。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何修行怖諸危難？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」飡那曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「菩薩之行其義如是。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王或見我，不見太子，必生憂惱，如致大病，其事云何？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a21_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今出家行菩提分法，布施、持戒、忍辱、精進、禪定、智慧，成就十力、四無所畏，豈令父母得不吉耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語已，即從座起合掌頂禮，舉手執劍如優鉢羅花葉，即自截髮擲虛空中。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "天主帝釋運大神力以手接髮，與諸天子安忉利天如法供養。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後有淨信婆羅門、長者、居士，於此山地起立塔廟。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時菩薩截髻髮已，問飡那曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝意云何？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947a29_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "可能住此同修行不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」飡那曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「王族之意不令住此，何敢固違。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩即以萬字福相百千威德之手，摩迦蹉迦馬王頂授菩提記，令彼飡那歸迦毘羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行七晝夜至二更初，到於城外園苑之中，王勅宮人眷屬至園迎接，唯見馬王，不見太子。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時宮嬪眷屬俱向馬前，抱馬王項，高聲啼哭。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦蹉迦馬聞是哭聲，心思太子悲淚傷痛，經須臾間迴顧兩邊即乃命終。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以宿因緣生六葉婆羅門家，利根結薄，聰明多智，太子成佛之後，即詣佛所聞法悟道，得無生忍。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時菩薩而復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今落髮作沙門相，云何身上得袈裟衣？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是念已，阿耨波摩城中有一長者，眷屬熾盛、財富無量如毘沙門，家有十子，人相端嚴，智慧聰利，俱樂出家，淨修梵行，因觀外境遷變無恒成辟支迦。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "父亡之後老母信重，製一袈裟施辟支迦。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "子白母曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我當不久入於涅槃。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此袈裟，我若受之無所使用，去此不遠有淨飯王子名悉達多，不久得成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，以此袈裟奉彼菩薩，能令老母得大果報。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說此語已運大神通，於虛空中現其雲雷、閃電、風雨，然後化火焚身入圓寂界。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時老母臨將捨壽，所持袈裟付與一女令奉菩薩。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此女忽然身得病患，臨無常時安置樹上，告樹神言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以此袈裟，與我奉彼淨飯王子悉達多。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時帝釋知是事已，自變其身為一獵士，手携弓劍披此袈裟，見太子來坐於路傍。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子問曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝是獵師，云何身上有此憍尸迦衣細妙法服，可以與我？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947b29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」獵人告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯此袈裟我非愛樂，今欲與汝是服微妙，恐人侵奪傷汝性命。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切世間知我威力，汝但施服勿懷憂慮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」帝釋天主即復本形頭面禮足，乃以袈裟奉上菩薩。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "授已即披與身不等，帝釋見衣不等，心自懷疑。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是念時，菩薩威神，令其袈裟與身相等。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c06_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忉利諸天歸命供養，婆羅門長者於後彼處建立塔廟，恒有苾芻往來禮拜。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時菩薩威儀具足，漸次經行，見一仙人名婆哩誐嚩，以手搘顋顏容不悅。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於意云何？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」仙人答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我此住處有多羅樹，花果繁盛其味甘香，忽然乾枯令我煩惱。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩復問：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「仙人住此本為修行，花果枯朽致愁悶耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」仙人聞已心忽惺悟，又見一菩薩色相端嚴，瞻仰戀慕而復問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝是出家菩薩不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝見分明。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」婆里誐嚩即斷疑惑法眼開淨，請菩薩坐，而以花果如法供養。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經須臾間，菩薩復問：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦毘羅城去此遠近？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」仙人答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「從茲至彼十二由旬。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「城邑不遙，如釋種來必作魔難。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即別仙人過殑伽河，往王舍城，以自工巧採取樹葉，作為鉢器，入城持鉢。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時民彌娑囉王在高樓上，遙見菩薩身相端嚴威儀寂靜，體挂法服手持應器巡門乞食，而興歎言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「王舍城中所住之人，無有如是威儀色相。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此苾芻，當非庶人下族之類，應是王種捨位出家，滅除罪業修持淨命。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時菩薩持鉢出城往一山中，以鉢置地端坐入定思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「民彌娑囉王見我發心，必有異意。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念時，王告大臣：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0947c29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我於樓上見一苾芻，身相端嚴威儀調順，非是庶人下族所生。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝當訪尋今在何處？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即時遣使往至山間，見此苾芻安詳而坐。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "國王知已躬自臨幸，接見瞻仰心生歡喜，因告言曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝之身貌甚是端嚴，若為苾芻不相宜稱，我有宮殿樓閣、嬪妃美女、最上富貴，與汝受用，勿作苾芻。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝身何姓？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a06_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何種族？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為我宣說。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「雪山相近有迦毘羅城，我之父王姓剎帝利，名曰淨飯，方理是國。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我須捨棄君父，為求菩提。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若是愚癡貪愛之人，假使世間并四大海滿中珍寶，猶尚不足；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大火然於乾薪，貪愛身心亦復如是。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀此物由如冤家，亦如毒蛇，一切憂惱怖畏根本。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使大風而能吹動一切諸山，於蘇迷盧終不能動；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使世間所有珍寶最上資財，國城、妻子、象馬、僮僕，而能惑亂一切人心，而於我心終不能動，唯涅槃解脫是真究竟。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時民彌娑囉王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今於此有何所求？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我求阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若成菩提願賜攝受。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王生歡喜復歸本處。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時菩薩往鷲峯山，山側非遙而有仙人勤修梵行，能以一足履地住經一日；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩聞之，亦以一足履地住經兩日。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "仙人復以五熱炙身立經一日；",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於是立經兩日。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼仙人互相驚怪降伏稱讚：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是修行，此是大沙門！",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a25_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝等修行，於何所求？",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」一云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我求帝釋。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」一云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a26_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我求梵王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」一云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我求魔界之身。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時菩薩即自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此仙人所修之行，皆是邪道，非我所依。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今於此不求帝釋、不求梵天、不求魔界，本為宿願利樂眾生，求成佛果。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道既非真，宜應捨彼。",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第五",
        "from": "T03n0191_005:0948b03_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]